The plugin allows to allow workers to send out weekly reports withing the
Cerberus Help Desk 5 gui.

=== INSTALLATION ===
- install and configure Cerberus Help Desk 5 (http://www.cerberusweb.com)
- download the code in <Cerb5>/storage/plugins/net.pixelinstrument.weekly_report
- activate the plugin under setup | Plugins & Features
